  "title": "Beauty Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Overseeing daily operations</li>\n  <li>Supervising staff and schedulling shifts</li>\n  <li>Deliver professional nail services including manicure/ pedicure, extension and gel nail services</li>\n  <li>Good excellent cleanliness and hygiene practices</li>\n  <li>Recommending various nail designs and nail art to clients</li>\n  <li>Evaluating the condition of clients’ nails and advising them on proper nail care and suitable nail care treatments</li>\n  <li>Sanitizing all nail instruments and equipment before each use</li>\n  <li>Ensuring that workstations are kept clean and orderly</li>\n  <li>Ensuring that nail supplies are adequately stocked</li>\n  <li>Advise clients on nail care and use of products and colors</li>\n  <li>Promote and sell nail care products</li>\n  <li>Schedule client appointments and accept payments</li>\n  <li>Other duties as and when assigned</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>With or Without experience - Candidates with experience will be an advantage</li>\n  <li>Able to work on weekends and PH</li>\n  <li>Good communication skills and cheerful personality</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Other Information:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Good and comfortable working environment</li>\n  <li>Annual leave and Medical benefits</li>\n  <li>Basic Salary + Commission + Service point + Incentive</li>\n</ul>",
